1st Game Goal should be simplest, can be a proof product. 
  Sticking in the 2D realm will allow for quicker achivement
  Using pixelation for quick asset builds (cheapest to outsource)(easiest to do on our own)
  Following platforming standards
  
  Progress Meter for learning goals
    1. Collison with enemies = death
    2. Introduce Melee combat
    3. Introdue ranged combat
  

